videos.headline: Holyfield stays in bounds for 24-yard TD run
videos.description: Elijah Holyfield charges down the sideline and somehow keeps himself in bounds before diving for the pylon to make it 14-3 Bulldogs.

videos.headline: Ridley tips pass to himself for TD catch
videos.description: Jake Fromm throws one up for Riley Ridley, who bobbles it before bringing it down between two defenders for a 10-yard touchdown reception.

videos.headline: Swift shows speed on 35-yard TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm swings one out to D'Andre Swift, who blazes by everyone en route to the end zone, giving Georgia a 28-6 lead.

videos.headline: Georgia RB recovers own fumble for TD
videos.description: Brian Herrien loses the ball in a goal-line scrum, but somehow finds it at the bottom of the pile for a touchdown to make it 38-6 Bulldogs.
